title: Episode 104 w/ Busy Bee  & Capone
itunes:title: Episode 104 w/ Busy Bee  & Capone
description:
N.O.R.E. and DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. In this episode the guys celebrate national hip hop month with the chief rocker Busy Bee along side Capone (of Capone-n-Noreaga). The guys talk the early days of hip hop and a lot more. --- Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/drinkchamps/support
